KL tin closes unchanged on short - covering . Malaysia ' s tin price closed unchanged at 14 . 29 ringgit ( $ 5 . 77 ) a kg on short - covering by European and local buyers despite an overnight fall on the London Metal Exchange ( LME ) , traders said . " There was buying at lower level and this helped the market close steady , otherwise it would have followed the LME , " said a trader . Final turnover was 87 tonnes , against 58 on Tuesday , and was absorved by European and Malaysian interests . The local price price was at a premium of $ 90 against LME , from $ 65 previously . - - K . Baranee Krishnaan ( 603 - 2307509 ) ( $ 1 = 2 . 4760 ) 
